name: The Default Cube
description:
This is a solo project based on the "Default cube" From blender. When you open up blender is there allways this default cube, that no one ever used so it just get delete. But what happen if you delete the cube. The cube will then get teleport in to the Default world, and there is a small mistake that you also can happpen to get in there by a mistake! But what if you get in there? What will the Default cube do? When it see you . After you  have delete it so many times over and over agien. I dont think it will be happen when  the Cube see you or maybe it will?!?! Find out by playing the game.

---------------------------------

Plz tell me what you feel about this game. A rate from 1 to 10.

And also why that rate. It will help a lot with feedback. 

So I can make better games in the future
